</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="728" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="20.[1467,2675,717,1341]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1467,1706,993,1026]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Fraternal Squirrel forages on the ground and lower levels of forest.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="728" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="20.[1467,2675,717,1341]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1468,2178,1075,1104]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
