</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="728" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="20.[1467,2675,717,1341]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1468,1819,1150,1183]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. The Fraternal Squirrel has a very limited extent of occurrence,its habitat is severely fragmented and it is experiencing a rapid and continuing population decline due to illegal logging. It is not known if it occurs in any protected areas.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
